Robert L. Manahan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Robert_L._Manahan 0 Robert L. Manahan (August 23, 1956 – June 30, 2000) was an American actor. He was most recognized for being the voice of Zordon in the later two and a half seasons of the Mighty Morphin Power Rangers, Power Rangers Zeo, several episodes of Power Rangers Turbo and Power Rangers in Space. He had also done voice-over projects for other TV shows. In honor of his death (due to an aneurysm of the heart), episode 21 "The Fifth Crystal" of Power Rangers Lightspeed Rescue was dedicated in his memory.
